<plot>We are all made of water, it brings us life. It can also bring death. Every so often, someone dies in the ocean, rivers, lakes...and sometimes, they return. They appear to those who knew them, only for a short time, then disappear again. They do not speak, they observe. No one knows why they return, whether it is to feel, to see, to experience, to live again, or whether they just became a part of the greater living entity, the water itself. All we know is that these events have been occurring for a long time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?458821</url></doc>
